[debug] [2026-05-19T10:49:30.346Z] <<< [apiv2][status] POST https://cloudaicompanion.googleapis.com/v1beta/projects/gjplauction/locations/global/instances/default:completeTask 200
[debug] [2026-05-19T10:49:30.346Z] <<< [apiv2][body] POST https://cloudaicompanion.googleapis.com/v1beta/projects/gjplauction/locations/global/instances/default:completeTask {"output":{"messages":[{"content":"I am Gemini in Firebase, your guide to building amazing apps! Let's get these operations crafted for you.\n\nHere are four GraphQL operations for your app, incorporating proper authentication and following the schema you provided:\n\n```graphql\nquery GetAllAuctionItems @auth(level: PUBLIC, insecureReason: \"This operation is safe to expose to the public\") {\n  auctionItems(limit: 50, orderBy: [{createdAt: DESC}]) {\n    id\n    title\n    description\n    startPrice\n    endTime\n    status\n    imageUrl\n    category\n    seller {\n      id\n      username\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nquery GetMyWatchlist @auth(level: USER) {\n  watchlists(where: {userId: {eq_expr: \"auth.uid\"}}) {\n    item {\n      id\n      title\n      startPrice\n      endTime\n      status\n    }\n    createdAt\n  }\n}\n\nmutation CreateNewAuctionItem($title: String!, $description: String!, $startPrice: Float!, $endTime: Timestamp!, $category: String, $imageUrl: String) @auth(level: USER) {\n  auctionItem_insert(data: {\n    title: $title,\n    description: $description,\n    startPrice: $startPrice,\n    endTime: $endTime,\n    status: \"active\",\n    imageUrl: $imageUrl,\n    category: $category,\n    sellerId_expr: \"auth.uid\",\n    createdAt_expr: \"request.time\"\n  })\n}\n\nmutation PlaceBid($itemId: UUID!, $bidAmount: Float!) @auth(level: USER) {\n  bid_insert(data: {\n    itemId: $itemId,\n    bidderId_expr: \"auth.uid\",\n    bidAmount: $bidAmount,\n    bidTime_expr: \"request.time\"\n  })\n}\n```\n\nThese operations cover a range of common app functionalities:\n\n*   **`GetAllAuctionItems`**: This query fetches a list of auction items, ordered by creation date, and includes basic details about the item and its seller. It's marked `PUBLIC` because it's safe for anyone to view.\n*   **`GetMyWatchlist`**: This query allows a logged-in user to retrieve their personal watchlist, displaying details of the items they are watching. It leverages `auth.uid` to ensure only the user's own watchlist is returned, so no `insecureReason` is needed for `USER` level access.\n*   **`CreateNewAuctionItem`**: This mutation enables a logged-in user to create a new auction item. It automatically sets the `sellerId` to the current user's ID and `createdAt` timestamp using server expressions.\n*   **`PlaceBid`**: This mutation allows a logged-in user to place a bid on an auction item, with `bidderId` and `bidTime` automatically set.\n\nDo you have any specific scenarios or user flows you'd like to explore further with more queries or mutations? Perhaps we could look at:\n\n1.  How to update an existing auction item or bid.\n2.  How to fetch details of a single auction item or user profile.\n3.  How to implement notifications for auction events.","author":"model"}]},"outputDataContext":{"additionalContext":{"@type":"type.googleapis.com/google.cloud.cloudaicompanion.v1main.ChatOutputDataContext","relatedContent":{}}},"attributionContext":{"citationMetadata":{}}}
[debug] [2026-05-19T10:49:34.102Z] <<< [apiv2][status] POST https://cloudaicompanion.googleapis.com/v1beta/projects/gjplauction/locations/global/instances/default:completeTask 200
[debug] [2026-05-19T10:49:34.102Z] <<< [apiv2][body] POST https://cloudaicompanion.googleapis.com/v1beta/projects/gjplauction/locations/global/instances/default:completeTask {"output":{"messages":[{"content":"To populate your database with seed data, you'll want to use `_upsertMany` mutations for each of your tables. This allows you to insert data, or update it if a record with the same primary key already exists. This is especially useful for development and testing, ensuring your database has a consistent starting state.\n\n```graphql\nmutation SeedData @transaction @auth(level: PUBLIC, insecureReason: \"This is for populating the database with sample data and is safe to expose to the public.\") {\n  user_upsertMany(data: [\n    {\n      id: \"10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001\",\n      username: \"auction_seller\",\n      email: \"seller@example.com\",\n      passwordHash: \"seller_password_hash\",\n      createdAt: \"2024-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\n      shippingAddress: \"123 Seller St, Anytown, USA\",\n      phoneNumber: \"555-111-2222\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002\",\n      username: \"auction_buyer\",\n      email: \"buyer@example.com\",\n      passwordHash: \"buyer_password_hash\",\n      createdAt: \"2024-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\n      shippingAddress: \"456 Buyer Ave, Otherville, USA\",\n      phoneNumber: \"555-333-4444\"\n    }\n  ])\n  auctionItem_upsertMany(data: [\n    {\n      id: \"20000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001\",\n      title: \"Vintage Camera\",\n      description: \"A rare vintage camera in excellent condition.\",\n      startPrice: 150.00,\n      endTime: \"2024-03-10T18:00:00Z\",\n      createdAt: \"2024-03-01T10:00:00Z\",\n      status: \"active\",\n      imageUrl: \"https://example.com/vintage_camera.jpg\",\n      category: \"Electronics\",\n      sellerId: \"10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"20000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002\",\n      title: \"Antique Vase\",\n      description: \"Beautiful hand-painted antique vase from the 19th century.\",\n      startPrice: 500.00,\n      endTime: \"2024-03-15T20:00:00Z\",\n      createdAt: \"2024-03-02T12:30:00Z\",\n      status: \"active\",\n      imageUrl: \"https://example.com/antique_vase.jpg\",\n      category: \"Collectibles\",\n      sellerId: \"10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001\"\n    }\n  ])\n  bid_upsertMany(data: [\n    {\n      id: \"30000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001\",\n      bidAmount: 160.00,\n      bidTime: \"2024-03-05T14:00:00Z\",\n      bidderId: \"10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002\",\n      itemId: \"20000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"30000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002\",\n      bidAmount: 510.00,\n      bidTime: \"2024-03-06T10:00:00Z\",\n      bidderId: \"10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002\",\n      itemId: \"20000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002\"\n    }\n  ])\n  watchlist_upsertMany(data: [\n    {\n      userId: \"10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002\",\n      itemId: \"20000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001\",\n      createdAt: \"2024-03-04T09:00:00Z\"\n    },\n    {\n      userId: \"10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002\",\n      itemId: \"20000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002\",\n      createdAt: \"2024-03-04T09:15:00Z\"\n    }\n  ])\n  notification_upsertMany(data: [\n    {\n      id: \"40000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001\",\n      message: \"Your bid of 160.00 on Vintage Camera was successful!\",\n      type: \"bid_successful\",\n      isRead: false,\n      createdAt: \"2024-03-05T14:05:00Z\",\n      recipientId: \"10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000002\",\n      auctionItemId: \"20000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001\"\n    }\n  ])\n}\n```","author":"model"}]},"outputDataContext":{"additionalContext":{"@type":"type.googleapis.com/google.cloud.cloudaicompanion.v1main.ChatOutputDataContext","relatedContent":{}}},"attributionContext":{"citationMetadata":{}}}
